"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"ええ、そうだったかと","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event223-07-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":227}],"windowDisplayName":"理事長","body":"自分の生活に密着した規則が預かり知らぬところで変更されたら、\n普通は少なからず反抗の意思を示すものです","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":227,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":227,"voiceId":"event223-07-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":227}],"windowDisplayName":"理事長","body":"しかし、あなたは違った。文句の１つも言うことなく、\n決定事項に従う……それは、なかなかできることではありません","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":227,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":227,"voiceId":"event223-07-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"納得しようがしまいが、ルールは守るもの。\nそれが、私の主義というだけです","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event223-07-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":227}],"windowDisplayName":